page.title: 20HOUSE TYPES-ARM/CANTLEY VILL
page.content: Arm/Cantley Vill=the Armthorpe and Cantley Village areas of this block. {GR 6204:}This contains a mixture of isolated C18/19th detached and terraced housing,and short terraced council housing,as well as bungalows and semi-detached housing in a modern private estate. {GR 6203:}This has an isolated farm. {GR 6202:}This square has C17/18/19th cottages and farmhouses with an estate and detached infilling of post 1970. {GR 6304:}This area has semi-detached houses and bungalows within council and private estates. {GR 6303 & 6302:}These have isolated farmhouses. {This block of the Domesday Project was {compiled by pupils and staff of {Armthorpe Comprehensive School and {Tranmoor Lane Junior School , {Armthorpe, Doncaster.
